{"tid":644471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國M男超愛櫻花妹　1年遊日2次找妹踩","createTime":"2018-04-27T09:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T09:19:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c812cb286864e9bcfe0e3d25a618720c93ee019c","tid":644471,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"日本網友「オロナ」在《推特》分享照片指出，他25日在東京澁谷車站外看到奇異景象，有一名男子趴在地上被女子踩頭。而有網友解釋說，這名男子其實在M男界很有名，他其實是位美國人，因為相當喜歡日本，加上被女子欺負的話會興奮，所以1年會遊日2次給日本妹踩，還曾經舔過日本女星水原希子的靴子。而這名美國男子名叫Lou，他也在《推特》分享他被日本妹踩，並且舔她靴子的照片，說「這是非常好吃的鞋子，真是一個於快的週四，不愧是東京阿」。<br />\n網友看到後紛紛留言「這個人我認識耶」、「竟然玩起野外PLAY了」、「現在出發過去好像來不及了」、「我對照片中右邊那位妹比較感興趣」、「一邊撫摸她的大腿一邊被踩才是樂趣阿」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180427/640_741eec1157a34242b04193e9f2bf687f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180427%2F640_741eec1157a34242b04193e9f2bf687f.jpg&h=0ad8029e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180427/640_ed30832439b93bdf09ac32ab6206dcc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180427%2F640_ed30832439b93bdf09ac32ab6206dcc0.jpg&h=c3949978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180427/640_08345267ebdd62c7b0ff8f86f638f272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180427%2F640_08345267ebdd62c7b0ff8f86f638f272.jpg&h=1ee1af08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180427/640_350bac316831c4e44209c028fe08cffc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180427%2F640_350bac316831c4e44209c028fe08cffc.jpg&h=2b9801ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180427/640_1385a6ffddc94a6ce5b5c60d